data.description: *** Price Improvement!*** With an assumable loan!!! Welcome to this charming 4 bedroom, 2 bath home nestled in the quiet Brighton Estate neighborhood in Killeen. This property offers a convenient location near the hospital, shopping centers, and dining establishments, ensuring a comfortable and vibrant lifestyle. As you step inside you will be greeted with an ample sized living area, formal and informal dining, and plenty of natural light. The 4 bedrooms offer enough space for relaxation and privacy with a split floorplan! Outside you'll discover an expansive, empty backyard that provides the perfect canvas for your creative vision and expertise. Spanning a generous size, this outdoor space offers endless possibilities for transforming it into a stunning oasis! Don't miss the opportunity to make this delightful home your own. Schedule a showing today!
